In the quhilk court comperit the abbot and a part of the conuent of Abirbrothoc and askit deliuerans of the mater of Balnamonysmyre conti- newit to this court wyth the consent of the said abbot and conuent on that a part and Symon Banerman of Elsyk on the tothir part · And than the schireff gart cal the said Symon Banerman til schaw his euidens and rychtis eftyr the tenour of the a& of court maid the xxxi day os O&ober last bypaffit in the tolbuth of Dunde · And than the said Symon oft tymis callit and nocht comperit til schaw ony evidens the schireff with the avise of the barronys forsaidis deliuerit the said abbot and conuent and thar ten- uandis and servandis til iois and bruke thair poffeffione of the south syid of Balnamonysmyre eftyr the tenour and forme of thair infeftmentis and euidentis maid til thaim thairapon for oucht that hes beyno schawyn as yeit in the contrare · And the copy of the proces decernyt til bath the parteis as afferis.
